Class BadAlien

  • java.lang.Object
    • MovingThing
      • BadAlien
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class BadAlien
extends MovingThing
    A class that represents a bouncing alien. This class inherits from MovingThing and allows the user to add functionality to the Alien class.
